s reachable.\",\"deterministic_setup\":[],\"agent_guidance\":\"No required environment or system properties. If tests deliberately cover OGNL's optional security-manager sandbox paths on JDK 25, make them conditional/tolerant of SecurityManager being disabled; do not require global setup for normal expression parsing, getValue/setValue, bean/property, method, constructor, collection, or Javassist-backed compiler coverage.\",\"risks\":[\"OGNL has optional SecurityManager-related behavior and system properties such as ognl.security.manager; those paths are fragile on modern JDKs and should not be treated as required setup for ordinary coverage.\",\"Tests that reflect into JDK internals or private JDK classes may need explicit JVM --add-opens, but meaningful OGNL coverage can use application fixture classes and avoid that requirement.\"]}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09c49389d6e35b59016a429394997c81939f845adefb3c184b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1589, "output": 753, "cacheRead": 48640, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 50982, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782748041396, "responseId": "resp_09c49389d6e35b59016a42938a52548193912151f88a6e35c4"}}
